video_title: CataractCoach™ 1087: how to perfect your case
detailed_steps: Side port creation at 8-10 oc position

video_title: CataractCoach™ 1087: how to perfect your case
detailed_steps: BSS (balanced salt solution) and anesthetic insertion

video_title: CataractCoach™ 1087: how to perfect your case
CataractCoach™ 1087: how to perfect your case
detailed_steps: Main port wound creation - 2 or 3 plane wound insertion created temporally  2 plane insertion: Angle blade upwards slightly first then insert blade horizontally into anterior chamber

video_title: CataractCoach™ 1087: how to perfect your case
detailed_steps: Creation of anterior capsulotomy with utrata forceps

video_title: CataractCoach™ 1087: how to perfect your case
detailed_steps: Insert cannula tip under anterior capsule and insert BSS to seperate lens from capsule   Signs of hydrodissection Wave  Nucleus lift  Nucleus prolapse

video_title: CataractCoach™ 1087: how to perfect your case
detailed_steps: Divide and conquer technique  Creation of trough - using phaco probe to create a central groove in the lens nucleus till it is deep enough to crack  A gauge of the depth is to be able to see a hint of the fundal red reflex  Phaco memory 1 setting

video_title: CataractCoach™ 1087: how to perfect your case
detailed_steps: Cracking of lens nucleus into 2 halves Place two instruments deep into the groove and separate the pieces horizontally

video_title: CataractCoach™ 1087: how to perfect your case
detailed_steps: Stop and chop Switch to phaco memory 2 setting (higher vacuum) Phaco probe holds the piece and 2nd instrument chops the lens half into smaller fragments  The small fragments are removed by the phaco probe

video_title: CataractCoach™ 1087: how to perfect your case
detailed_steps: Irrigation and aspiration of soft lens material with I/A Probe

video_title: CataractCoach™ 1087: how to perfect your case
detailed_steps: Insert OVD to fill the capsular bag

video_title: CataractCoach™ 1087: how to perfect your case
detailed_steps: Use injector to insert lens into capsular bag   +/- sinksy hook to stabilise the eye and provide counter traction

video_title: CataractCoach™ 1087: how to perfect your case
detailed_steps: Rotate the lens into the capsular bag

video_title: CataractCoach™ 1087: how to perfect your case
detailed_steps: Use I/A probe to aspirate viscoat from bag and angles of the eye

video_title: CataractCoach™ 1087: how to perfect your case
detailed_steps: Hydrate the side ports and main port wounds using BSS cannula
